title: Findgo 1.2.15 - Directory & Listing WordPress Theme
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org If there are no seeds, use our forum for direct download links! Findgo WordPress Theme is a listing directory WordPress template that will help you create, manage and monetize a local or global directory site. Feel free to set your own goal and get your favourite spots listed online! Findgo WordPress Theme Features [*]Add a listing in frontend [*]Claim a listing [*]Make a reservation [*]Book an appointment [*]5 Listing Layout (Half Map, Grid, List) [*]5 Listing detail layout [*]Add Listing to favorite [*]Review listing [*]Reply a review [*]5 Homes page layouts [*]Footer builder: easy to create or edit footer [*]WooCommerce 3.0 Ready
